===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Boötes'''

#{{constellation}}: A [[circumpolar]] [[constellation]] of the [[northern]] sky, called the "bear-guard" or the "[[herdsman]]". It includes the third brightest star in the night sky [[Arcturus]].

